    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi. Papa et imperatore nondum hab[emu]s,
                        defuncto Heinrico imperatore filio quondam Chunradi imperatoris, sub anno
                        dominice incarnationis millesimo quinquagesi[mo] octavo, die quarta mensis
                        madii, indic(ione) undecima, <placeName ref="#places/594"
                            >RAV(enne)</placeName>. Pecii a te quidem in Dei nomine d[omno]
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1597">Albizone</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Casalia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Fruits/vegetables #Rivers #Rent_in_money #Books #Penalty #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters #Landed_possessions #Cereals #Maiores #Minores #Linen #Forests #Fisheries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460"><placeName key="#Monasteries"
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposiani</placeName></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> consenc(ientibus) eiusdem monasterii
                        mo(na)h(is), uti mihi presenti in Christi nomine <persName><name
                                ref="Corbus/de Medio Gauro">Corbulo qui vocor de <placeName
                                    ref="#places/4685">Medio Gauro</placeName></name></persName>
                        petitori pro me seu filiis meis, <rs key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis"
                            >libelli nomine</rs>, con[ce]disti nobis rem iuris suprascripti
                        monasterii nostri, idest <rs key="#Casalia">casale</rs> unum in integrum
                        quod fuit olim de <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petro</name></persName> de
                            <rs key="#Priests">presbitero</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Martinus">Martino</name></persName>, positum in loco
                        qui dicitur Medio Gauro, cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs> , <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>,
                            <rs>salictis</rs>, <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >venacionibus</rs>, <rs key="#Fisheries">piscacionibus</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aucupacionibus</rs> usque
                        ad <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables">nespolum</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"><rs key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos"
                                >pantano</rs> de Sancto Georgio</placeName> usque veniente in
                            <placeName>fronte</placeName> et cum omnibus predicto casali
                        pertinentibus, secundum quod prefatus Petrus habuit et tenuit, <rs
                            key="#Confinia">inter affines</rs> eius loci ubi reiacet prefatum
                        casalem cum omnibus sibi pertinentibus: a primo latere <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvius</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Confinia #Rivers" ref="#places/3563">Gaurus</placeName> , a
                        secundo <placeName key="#Confinia #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">polisinum de
                            supra</placeName>, a tercio fronte de supra atque a quarto latere iuris
                            <orgName key="#Confinia">Sancti Petri</orgName>. Habendum, tenendum,
                        laborandum, restaurandum et in omnibus meliorandum in annis advenientibus
                        viginti et novem ad renovandum. Sub <rs key="#Levies">terratici</rs> omnium
                            <rs key="#Cereals #Maiores">mai[orum] laborum</rs> modio quinto, <rs
                            key="#Cereals #Minores">minutorum</rs> modio octavo, <rs key="#Linen"
                            >lini</rs> manna nona, omni festivitate Sancte Marie medii augusti <rs
                            key="#Rent_in_money">denarios Veneticos duodecim tantum</rs>. Pervectis
                        omnibus a nobis [usque] ad ripam Gauri, cum fide et humilitate sine fraude
                        aut malo ingenio. [Id]eo quia accepisti call(ciarii) nomine idest <rs
                            key="#Books">librum</rs> unum pro <rs key="#Price">denariorum
                            Veneticorum solidis quadraginta</rs>. Et tu iamdictus ordinator cum tuis
                        successoribus mihi meisque filiis auctoriare et defensare promisisti. Si
                        quis vero partis nostre contra hanc peticionem ire tenta[verit] ante
                        prefinitum tempus quod superius legitur det pars parti fidem servanti ante
                        omne litis inicium aut interpell(acionem), pene nomine, <rs key="#Penalty"
                            >auri uncias duas</rs> et post pene sol(ucionem) maneat hec peticionem
                        firma. QUAm vero paginam <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Wido"
                                >Widonem</name></persName> Dei misericordia <rs key="#Tabellio"
                            >tabellionem</rs> Rav(ennatem) scribendum rogavi sub die menseque et
                        anno atque indic(ione) suprascripta undecima, RAV(enne). Signum manus
                        Corbuli de Medio Gauro petitoris ad omnia suprascripta.</ab>
